# Copy to frontend/.env.local (gitignored) for local development.
#
# Worker API — use production worker, or run `npm run dev:worker` and point here:
# VITE_WORKER_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787
#
# LaunchDarkly — use the `test` environment client-side ID locally:
# VITE_LAUNCHDARKLY_CLIENT_SIDE_ID=6a4e663319d3db0a5e25b9d1
#
# Supabase overrides (optional — defaults in src/lib/env.ts match production):
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://nmwlebcvezybfwertlzs.supabase.co
# After custom Auth domain is active, you can use:
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://auth.tee-time.io
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key
